name: A new user correctly register in uTest

testSteps.description: Given that the user is on the uTest singUp page

children.description: Ricardo open up utest
Ricardo opens the Utest home page
Ricardo clicks on New user register button

testSteps.description:
When the user provides the required personal information in each step
| strFirstName | strLastName | strEmail | strBirthMonth | strBirthDay | strBirthYear | strCity | strZip | strCountry | strComputerOs | strOsVersion | strOsLanguage | strMobileBrand | strMobileModel | strMobileOs | strPassword |
| *random name* | *random lastname* | *random email* | June | 14 | 1999 | Neiva | 140414 | Colombia | Windows | Windows 10 | Spanish | Apple | Iphone X | iOS 12.0 | <random password> |

children.description: Ricardo fill personal
Ricardo enters 'Janis' into where you enter your first name
Ricardo enters 'Kuhlman' into where you enter your last name
Ricardo enters 'cletus.turner@yahoo.com' into where you enter your email
Ricardo select June on where you enter your birth month
Ricardo select 14 on where you enter your birth day
Ricardo select 1999 on where you enter your birth year
Ricardo clicks on button that loads the Location forms
Ricardo fill address
Ricardo enters 'Neiva' into where you enter your city
Ricardo types 'ARROW_DOWN' in where you enter your city
Ricardo types 'ENTER' in where you enter your city
Ricardo enters '140414' into where you enter your zip or postal code
Ricardo clicks on Container that opens the country list
Ricardo enters 'Colombia' into where you enter your country
Ricardo clicks on button that loads the devices page
Ricardo fill devices
Ricardo clicks on container that allows display the computer os
Ricardo enters 'Windows' then hits [ENTER] into where you enter your computer OS
Ricardo clicks on container that allows display the computer os version
Ricardo enters 'Windows 10' then hits [ENTER] into where you enter your computer OS version
Ricardo clicks on container that allows display the computer os language
Ricardo enters 'Spanish' then hits [ENTER] into where you enter your computer OS language
Ricardo clicks on container that allows display the mobile brand
Ricardo enters 'Apple' then hits [ENTER] into where you enter your mobile brand
Ricardo clicks on container that allows display the mobile model
Ricardo enters 'Iphone X' then hits [ENTER] into where you enter your mobile model
Ricardo clicks on container that allows display the mobile model
Ricardo enters 'iOS 12.0' then hits [ENTER] into where you enter your mobile model
Ricardo clicks on button that loads the last step
Ricardo fill security
Ricardo enters '<random password>' into where you enter your password
Ricardo enters '<random password>' into where you confirm your password
Ricardo clicks on where you check to active rhe news letter option
Ricardo clicks on where you check to confirm terms of use
Ricardo clicks on where you check to confirm privacy and security policy
Ricardo clicks on button that sends the form information

testSteps.description:
Then the welcome uTest page should display
| strWelcomeText |
| Welcome to the world's largest community of freelance software testers! |
